product_name: IT CosmeticsSuperhero No-Tug Longwear Eyeshadow Stick
summary: SummaryIt Cosmetics Superhero No-Tug Longwear Eyeshadow Sticks are everything you love about eyeshadow, now in an easy-to-use cream shadow stick! This super blendable eyeshadow stick glides onto your lids without tugging on your delicate eye area. Available in matte and pearl finishes!
details: DetailsBenefitsInnovative waterproof eyeshadow stick glides on super blendable pigment without tugging on your delicate eye areaProvides comfortable, all-day wear; suitable for sensitive eyesFormulated with tri-peptide complex, hydrolyzed collagen and caffeine, this lid-loving long-wear cream shadow gives you younger-looking eyes instantlyAvailable in 14 buildable pearl and matte shadesKey IngredientsFormulated with tri-peptide complex, hydrolyzed collagen and caffeine, this cream eyeshadow stick glides on smoothly for younger-looking eyes instantlyFeatures16 Hour Wear90% says it applies evenly*85% say it visibly smooths texture of eyelids*Crease-proof Brighter-Looking Eyes*Based on a 1 week consumer studyItem 2589858How To UseSwipe Superhero No-Tug Waterproof Eyeshadow Stick onto your eyelids for super smooth, super blendable, super all-day wear results. Use your fingertips to blend effortlessly. Complete your super eye transformation with Superhero No-Tug Sharpenable Gel Eyeliner and Superhero Elastic Stretch Volumizing and Lengthening Mascara!IngredientsPearl Shades: Methyl Trimethicone, Trimethylsiloxysilicate, Polyethylene, Silica [Nano] / Silica, Synthetic Fluorphlogopite, Synthetic Wax, Sorbitan Olivate, Calcium Aluminum Borosilicate, Calcium Titanium Borosilicate, Ethylene/Propylene Copolymer, Polyglyceryl-2 Triisostearate, Aqua / Water / Eau, Tin Oxide, Glycerin, Butylene Glycol, Ceteareth-25, Tocopherol, Caffeine, Sodium Hyaluronate, Ascorbic Acid, Hydrolyzed Collagen, Cetyl Alcohol, Carbomer, Sodium Lactate, Phenoxyethanol, Ceramide Np, Behenic Acid, Cholesterol, Polysorbate 20, Ceramide Ns, Ethylhexylglycerin, Ceramide Ap, Ceramide Eop, Ceramide Eos, Caprooyl Phytosphingosine, Caprooyl Sphingosine, Ascorbyl Palmitate, Palmitoyl Tripeptide-1, Palmitoyl Tetrapeptide-7, [+/-: Mica, CI 77891 / Titanium Dioxide, CI 77491, CI 77499 / Iron Oxides, CI 75470 / Carmine, CI 77510 / Ferric Ferrocyanide].Shipping & Coupon RestrictionsThis brand is excluded from most Ulta Beauty coupons.See brand eligibility details
how_to_use: Swipe Superhero No-Tug Waterproof Eyeshadow Stick onto your eyelids for super smooth, super blendable, super all-day wear results. Use your fingertips to blend effortlessly. Complete your super eye transformation with Superhero No-Tug Sharpenable Gel Eyeliner and Superhero Elastic Stretch Volumizing and Lengthening Mascara!

reviews.headline: Meh
reviews.comments: Luckily I got this on a 50% promo but what it would have cost full price, not super impressed. The colors are more of a sheer shimmer and in my opinion don't show that well.

reviews.headline: Great
reviews.comments: Nice coverage, goes on smooth. It just looks beautiful and blends well while maintaining its coverage. Doesn't look cakey, like some cream eye shadows do. Perfect.

reviews.headline: Love it. Will try different colors
reviews.comments: This is a really nice product. The shimmer is lovely. The reason I'm not giving it 5 stars is that the color pay off is very light.  Very pretty amethyst shade.

reviews.headline: Awesome color
reviews.comments: Lasts all day and the color is beautiful

reviews.headline: So Happy with This Eyeshadow Stick
reviews.comments: I've used various eyeshadow sticks over the years and have been looking for one again. Decided to try this during the 21 days of beauty sale. I love it & wish I'd bought another one while it was on sale. The color (Transformative Taupe) is exactly what I'd been searching for. It works great as a base color on my eyes & I like that it's not too dark (I'm pale). It glides on very easily and stays put. It's also easy to spread around with my fingers and doesn't make me need to tug or press too hard. I'm 53 so I'm mindful of trying to be more gentle with my skin these days. Just a very good product that I'll definitely buy again. My only concern is if it will break off, as some other brands tend to do. Hoping that it won't as long as I continue to only twist up a little at a time and am gentle when applying.

reviews.headline: Lives Up to its Name
reviews.comments: Bold Bubbly is a shimmering champagne that brightens up the inner corner of the eye. It applies easily (No-Tug) but still has staying power. This is the 2nd color I've bought and I'll probably order another. I've found that a lot of eyeshadow sticks break but this one does not.

reviews.headline: Game changer!
reviews.comments: These superhero sticks are absolutely foolproof. They are blendable and the colors are beautiful.

reviews.headline: Hard to blend
reviews.comments: This pencil was so hard to blend. The colors are pretty but you really have to work fast and tug at the delicate skin on your eyes. I returned.

reviews.headline: I would buy this product again.
reviews.comments: Easty to apply; great color..

reviews.headline: I would buy this product again.
reviews.comments: Covers well; easy to apply.

reviews.headline: I love these! But blending…. Meh
reviews.comments: I love these shadow sticks. They work and stay all day (unless you rub them, then they may rub off). I love to layer the colors and this amethyst addition is fantastic! Will definitely purchase again!

reviews.headline: DOES NOT CREASE!!
reviews.comments: I have super oily skin and I am ALWAYS creased by the end of my work day. I am so thankful Joan demonstrated the No Tug for me!

reviews.headline: LOVE IT!
reviews.comments: This is my first purchase of this eyeshadow and can I say WOW!  Lasts till the end of the day!

reviews.headline: Love these eyeshadow sticks!
reviews.comments: I never really wore eyeshadow- always used powder.  Since I've been using Superhero eyeshadow sticks, I am LOVING how easy they are to apply. I would definitely recommend them highly!

reviews.headline: Doesn't show up on my light skin
reviews.comments: Maybe if you have either very fair skin or darker skin you'd be able to see these, but I loaded up on several different shades in light and even medium tones (mauve, taupe, etc.), and the only ones I can see are the slate one and the purple one. What a waste of money. They do go on nicely and they do blend well, FWIW.

reviews.headline: These should not be advertised as matte with so much glitter
reviews.comments: I purchased these for my mom who detests glitter and thought I would be safe with the matte shades but they are loaded with glitter. Well at least in the 2 matte shades I bought which were tough tan and courageous cream. I could not find anywhere in any of the descriptions where it says there is glitter in the matte shades. The photos and videos do not really show the glitter either. Only after reading some of the reviews did I find other complaints mentioning the glitter. It's not a bad product,  just needs a more accurate description.

reviews.headline: Love the purple color
reviews.comments: The eyeshadow goes on smoothly. If you want heavier color, you press harder during application. Color is deep enough to be seen and is not a light shade. Recommend this brand.

reviews.headline: Great shadow stick
reviews.comments: I've bean leaning toward shadow sticks lately and these are great and have a good color selection. Seems a bit stronger than others thus halting breakage

reviews.headline: I love this Eyeshadow Stick!
reviews.comments: I wanted something that would apply easily and stay on without melting or looking to pasty (like dry shadows) for my older eyes. This works great and I carry one for my travel  - quick to apply and off I go. I also have some eyeshadow sticks from Laura Mercier and like them as well, but this is the perfect matte color for me. For this purchase it was for my Aunt who is visually impaired. I showed her how to apply it and she is very happy because putting on eye shadow was challenging - she loves the ease of use and the even application.

reviews.headline: Yes I would definitely buy this again!
reviews.comments: It is so easy to apply and stays put all day..
